      <data key="edge_color">#DC143C</data>
      <data key="edge_confidence">MEDIUM</data>
      <data key="edge_mechanism">BRC1 lowers the basal (non-polar) rate of auxin efflux from buds; in Arabidopsis BRC1 does not directly transcriptionally target PIN3 (unlike cucumber), instead acting on broader efflux machinery and via auxin conjugation through GH3.5.</data>
